message: #8567 My dream is to get fifty gallons of ice cream and to consume it all in one sitting.

#8565 One time, I was staying at a hotel for an overnight math competition. At the event was a boy who had sent me a friend request a few weeks ago (which I did not accept because I heard he was creepy). Once, he cornered me in the hotel and made me friend him. I didn't think much of it at the time, but now I realize that was extremely creepy. And yet, I'm also relieved he didn't do anything worse.
#8564 You looked so much cuter when your hair was longer. :(

#8559 To the guy who tried to use his crutches to prop open the second set of doors for me after I held open the first door for him, thank you for making me laugh and for totally making my day with your thoughtfulness :) I wish you a speedy recovery!

#8556 Worst part of being a super senior: your class of 2016 league buddies are scattered all over different time zones, and it's harder to get all these assholes together and play a ranked game in league. 

Best part being a super senior: you don't have to share a laundry machine with said assholes anymore.
